{
  "stem": "24958.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My apartment was not in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They gave us a room somewhere down [INAUDIBLE] Street in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember like it was yesterday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we moved in, we were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My husband played there in the ghetto in a-- in a restaurant for the Jews, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you say you couldn't go to your apartment, was it--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was forbidden.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Forbidden.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were signs that you-- you can go only in this and this district.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was lost.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1940 maybe, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It must have been the winter, probably in the wintertime, I image, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I imagine in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we wanted to-- then they came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They almost surrounded the-- they built a-- a wall around the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were going to close up the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we didn't want to be in the closed ghetto, so we ran away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we took off our things, and we-- we went to the train, and we  went back to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my-- in Krakow, we couldn't be anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My in-laws were in a small town called [INAUDIBLE], so we went there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, the Krakow ghetto came much later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After this, there was a-- there was a rule that the Jews had to live 30 kilometers away from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my-- my in-laws were already in a little town, so we went there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went there, and we were living there for a few months by some Polish farmers in a room till-- till the ghetto time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then game the rules that all Jews had to move to Krakow to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to move to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- that was maybe 1940, 1941 probably.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
